{"tid":828450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打完風，得我一個有牛皮膠紙漬問題?","createTime":"2018-09-19T16:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T14:15:06.000Z","uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"7836e83d6abb54a00289a1f35adbeadddd8bf717","tid":828450,"uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:33:35.000Z","msg":"上網揾過，主要有幾個方法:<br />\n1) 黏膠去除劑(eg: 3M /  保賜利（Botny）)<br />\n2) WD40<br />\n3) 松節水<br />\n4) 風筒加熱<br />\n5) 75%/95% 酒精<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個人試過風筒同埋75%酒精，唔多得，聽日會試黏膠去除劑，<br />\n有冇人有經驗可以推介下邊個牌子?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS: 提提未撕膠紙嘅巴絲，愈遲撕就愈難清，避免陽光直射玻璃窗上令膠紙受熱而膠質溶解"},{"pid":"e609831dd5afa36aa9b8e3fb695a08dbe401269a","tid":828450,"uid":38540,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"係 因為根本唔會用牛皮膠紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0b6e2d5665240afe1f6b3cc58590fc844d710a","tid":828450,"uid":68598,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"點解唔用皺紋膠紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf5e7dc6632c8b05af7126a7611ba85b2301155","tid":828450,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"過埋十月先清啦，九月都未完風季"},{"pid":"fb294dba3f834fd7441d6d21b5895768c1580011","tid":828450,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"WD40 已經可以<br />\n唔使試其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b90446b0568744e7c779c1df14d177acbe09336","tid":828450,"uid":1425,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"打完風個日就要清啦, 一比太陽曬就乜都留漬"},{"pid":"700616c95ad346074a244b96df837419f0b24973","tid":828450,"uid":92690,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"要用松節水"},{"pid":"d6502fb668b23f48702c210dc99129359791a7fa","tid":828450,"uid":125813,"like":1,