f828919d55d90b092703481d3d5312e","tid":828450,"uid":70769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"3m 皺紋膠紙都係12蚊卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caa6335bef72a4fe5b4de5cbcb7b3f41bd0ba79","tid":828450,"uid":60299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b0bb9ced0dddfaa31eba61ef602e8cdda7f7af8","tid":828450,"uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:10:29.000Z","msg":"做完功課<br />\n<br />\n松節油 主要成分 C10H16<br />\n白電油 主要成分是含5到11個碳原子的鏈烷、環烷或芳烴<br />\nWD-40 主要成分係50% Stoddard solvent，其主要成分係C6H14<br />\n以上用極性黎講係都無極性溶劑<br />\n<br />\n3M Sticker Cleaner 主要成分Methyl Acetate <br />\n火酒 主要成分C3H8O<br />\n都係極性溶劑<br />\n<br />\n基於試過火酒，好似唔係好Work，聽日應該會買支WD-40試下先，唔啱用都可以用黎上吓D鋁窗"},{"pid":"d99c972b12c2ef9379dfc4bb2fb1aefc61e090f6","tid":828450,"uid":101917,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:11:50.000Z","msg":"成個窗換啦屌"},{"pid":"aafaf6b35baa7a828f1b4c014e9c05420b9be995","tid":828450,"uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9caa6335bef72a4fe5b4de5cbcb7b3f41bd0ba79","tid":828450,"uid":60299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:12:47.000Z","msg":"我打算2種一齊用，反正刀片都唔貴<br />\n就係驚會整花D玻璃窗<br />\n<br />\n以巴打嘅經驗黎講，會唔會好易整花?"},{"pid":"5fdc1d2b2f462c7dfce5cc12cb4b3b63a78f0acc","tid":828450,"uid":82183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1b7c5b6df828919d55d90b092703481d3d5312e","tid":828450,"uid":70769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"3m 皺紋膠紙都係12蚊卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:17:56.000Z","msg":"打風果日先急Call我，我去到果時天都黑埋，無時間揾好膠紙，成18蚊1Pack低質膠紙呀"},{"pid":"0fb2afe8460222b065e2227fd97951407917b796","tid":828450,"uid":50801,"like":0,